**Financial Ratios:**`price_earnings_ttm`, `price_book_fq`, `debt_to_equity_fq`, `current_ratio_fq`

**Performance:**`Perf.1D`, `Perf.W`, `Perf.1M`, `Perf.3M`, `Perf.YTD`, `Perf.Y`

